### ✅ ORDER CHECKOUT THROUGHPUT TEST REQUESTS
### File này có thể dùng với REST Client extension trong VS Code
### Hoặc copy vào Postman/Thunder Client

### 1. Test Checkout Throughput (1000 orders)
POST http://localhost:8005/v1/test/checkout/throughput
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalOrders": 1000,
  "batchSize": 100,
  "addressId": "test-address-1",
  "paymentMethod": "COD"
}

###

